v><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p>输出结果：</p>\n<div class=\"language- line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"\" data-title=\"\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span>开始</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>结束</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>Promise 1</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>Promise 2</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span>setTimeout</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><p><strong>分析</strong>：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>首先执行同步代码，输出&quot;开始&quot;</li>\n<li>遇到<code v-pre>setTimeout</code>，将其回调放入宏任务队列</li>\n<li>遇到<code v-pre>Promise</code>，将其<code v-pre>then</code>回调放入微任务队列</li>\n<li>输出&quot;结束&quot;</li>\n<li>调用栈清空，执行微任务队列中的任务，输出&quot;Promise 1&quot;</li>\n<li>第一个<code v-pre>then</code>产生了第二个<code v-pre>then</code>，将其放入微任务队列并执行，输出&quot;Promise 2&quot;</li>\n<li>微任务队列清空，执行宏任务队列中的<code v-pre>setTimeout</code>回调，输出&quot;setTimeout&quot;</li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"案例2-复杂的执行顺序\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#案例2-复杂的执行顺序\"><span>案例2：复杂的执行顺序</span></a></h4>\n<div class=\"language-javascript line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"javascript\" data-title=\"javascript\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">console</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-